{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852604433,"sessionID":"ses_286eff5b1ffe08nasfTV6hQ3cQ","part":{"id":"prt_d79104800001viJYqlRMIm3Kj6","messageID":"msg_d791035f8001pn0Nc2bT3XSZsy","sessionID":"ses_286eff5b1ffe08nasfTV6hQ3cQ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_b52b74153d8441ffb9390b84","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-001/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-001/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-001 ŌĆö CRD AgentRuntime ń▒╗Õ×ŗÕ«Üõ╣ē\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRD type definitions in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`.\n6: \n7: ## Base Specifications\n8: \n9: - **AR**: AR-001\n10: - **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n11: - **Language**: Go\n12: - **Size**: S\n13: - **Base Spec**: `deployment/client-go.md` (client-go library types)\n14: \n15: ---\n16: \n17: ## Scenario: AgentRuntime Type Definition\n18: \n19: ### AR-001-001: AgentRuntime type with required spec fields\n20: \n21: - **GIVEN** a Go package at `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n22: - **WHEN** defining `AgentRuntime` struct with kubebuilder markers\n23: - **THEN** the type SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta`\n24: - **AND** SHALL include `Spec` field of type `AgentRuntimeSpec`\n25: - **AND** SHALL include `Status` field of type `AgentRuntimeStatus`\n26: \n27: ### AR-001-002: AgentRuntimeSpec required fields\n28: \n29: - **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct definition\n30: - **WHEN** defining the spec fields\n31: - **THEN** `MaxSessionDuration` SHALL be `string` type, required, default `\"8h\"`\n32: - **AND** `SessionTimeout` SHALL be `string` type, required, default `\"15m\"`\n33: - **AND** `TargetPort` SHALL be `[]TargetPort` type, required, non-empty\n34: \n35: ### AR-001-003: AgentRuntime optional podTemplate\n36: \n37: - **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeSpec` definition\n38: - **WHEN** `podTemplate` field is specified\n39: - **THEN** it SHALL be of type `PodTemplateSpec` (custom, not corev1.PodTemplateSpec)\n40: - **AND** SHALL be optional (omitempty)\n41: \n42: ### AR-001-004: AgentRuntimeStatus with conditions\n43: \n44: - **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeStatus` struct definition\n45: - **WHEN** defining status subresource\n46: - **THEN** it SHALL include `Conditions` of type `[]metav1.Condition`\n47: - **AND** SHALL include `ObservedGeneration` of type `int64`\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## Scenario: CodeInterpreter Type Definition\n52: \n53: ### AR-001-005: CodeInterpreter type definition\n54: \n55: - **GIVEN** a Go package at `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n56: - **WHEN** defining `CodeInterpreter` struct with kubebuilder markers\n57: - **THEN** the type SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta`\n58: - **AND** SHALL include `Spec` field of type `CodeInterpreterSpec`\n59: - **AND** SHALL include `Status` field of type `CodeInterpreterStatus`\n60: \n61: ### AR-001-006: CodeInterpreterSpec fields\n62: \n63: - **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct definition\n64: - **WHEN** defining spec fields\n65: - **THEN** `AuthMode` SHALL be of type `AuthMode` (enum: \"picod\", \"none\"), optional, default `\"picod\"`\n66: - **AND** `MaxSessionDuration` SHALL be `string` type, optional, default `\"8h\"`\n67: - **AND** `SessionTimeout` SHALL be `string` type, optional, default `\"15m\"`\n68: - **AND** `Ports` SHALL be `[]TargetPort` type, optional\n69: - **AND** `Template` SHALL be of type `ContainerTemplateSpec`, required\n70: - **AND** `WarmPoolSize` SHALL be `int32` type, optional, default `0`\n71: \n72: ### AR-001-007: CodeInterpreterStatus with ready field\n73: \n74: - **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterStatus` struct definition\n75: - **WHEN** defining status subresource\n76: - **THEN** it SHALL include `Conditions` of type `[]metav1.Condition`\n77: - **AND** SHALL include `ObservedGeneration` of type `int64`\n78: - **AND** SHALL include `Ready` of type `bool`\n79: \n80: ---\n81: \n82: ## Scenario: Shared Type Definitions\n83: \n84: ### AR-001-008: TargetPort type\n85: \n86: - **GIVEN** shared type definitions in `types.go`\n87: - **WHEN** defining `TargetPort` struct\n88: - **THEN** it SHALL include `Port` of type `int32`, required\n89: - **AND** SHALL include `Protocol` of type `string` (HTTP/HTTPS)\n90: - **AND** SHALL include `Name` of type `string`, optional\n91: - **AND** SHALL include `PathPrefix` of type `string`, optional\n92: \n93: ### AR-001-009: PodTemplateSpec type\n94: \n95: - **GIVEN** shared type definitions in `types.go`\n96: - **WHEN** defining `PodTemplateSpec` struct\n97: - **THEN** it SHALL include `metav1.ObjectMeta` for metadata\n98: - **AND** SHALL include `Spec` field of type `PodSpec` (selective fields from corev1.PodSpec)\n99: \n100: ### AR-001-010: ContainerTemplateSpec type\n101: \n102: - **GIVEN** shared type definitions in `types.go`\n103: - **WHEN** defining `ContainerTemplateSpec` struct\n104: - **THEN** it SHALL include `Image` of type `string`, required\n105: - **AND** SHALL include `Command` of type `[]string`, optional\n106: - **AND** SHALL include `Args` of type `[]string`, optional\n107: - **AND** SHALL include `Env` of type `[]corev1.EnvVar`, optional\n108: - **AND** SHALL include `Resources` of type `corev1.ResourceRequirements`, optional\n109: - **AND** SHALL include `RuntimeClassName` of type `*string`, optional\n110: \n111: ### AR-001-011: AuthMode enum\n112: \n113: - **GIVEN** type definitions in `types.go`\n114: - **WHEN** defining `AuthMode` type\n115: - **THEN** it SHALL be a string type with kubebuilder validation: `enum:picod,enum:none`\n116: - **AND** default value SHALL be `\"picod\"`\n117: \n118: ---\n119: \n120: ## Scenario: Scheme Registration\n121: \n122: ### AR-001-012: Register types to scheme\n123: \n124: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` package\n125: - **WHEN** creating `register.go`\n126: - **THEN** it SHALL define `SchemeGroupVersion` as `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n127: - **AND** SHALL provide `addKnownTypes` function to register `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `CodeInterpreter`, `CodeInterpreterList`\n128: - **AND** SHALL implement `AddToScheme` function for scheme registration\n129: \n130: ### AR-001-013: Package documentation\n131: \n132: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` package\n133: - **WHEN** creating `doc.go`\n134: - **THEN** it SHALL include package-level kubebuilder markers: `// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, `// +versionName=v1alpha1`\n135: \n136: ---\n137: \n138: ## Scenario: DeepCopy Generation\n139: \n140: ### AR-001-014: DeepCopy methods generation\n141: \n142: - **GIVEN** Go types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n143: - **WHEN** running `make generate` (controller-gen)\n144: - **THEN** `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` SHALL be generated\n145: - **AND** SHALL include `DeepCopyInto`, `DeepCopy` methods for `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `CodeInterpreter`, `CodeInterpreterList`\n146: - **AND** SHALL include DeepCopy methods for all nested types: `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, `CodeInterpreterSpec`, `CodeInterpreterStatus`, `TargetPort`, `PodTemplateSpec`, `ContainerTemplateSpec`\n147: \n148: ### AR-001-015: DeepCopy for lists\n149: \n150: - **GIVEN** list types in `types.go`\n151: - **WHEN** running controller-gen\n152: - **THEN** `AgentRuntimeList.DeepCopy()` SHALL return a copy with `Items` slice properly copied\n153: - **AND** `CodeInterpreterList.DeepCopy()` SHALL return a copy with `Items` slice properly copied\n154: \n155: ---\n156: \n157: ## Scenario: CRD Generation\n158: \n159: ### AR-001-016: CRD YAML generation for AgentRuntime\n160: \n161: - **GIVEN** `AgentRuntime` type with kubebuilder markers\n162: - **WHEN** running `make gen-crd`\n163: - **THEN** CRD YAML SHALL be generated in `manifests/charts/base/crds/`\n164: - **AND** SHALL have `name: agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n165: - **AND** SHALL have `spec.scope: Namespaced`\n166: - **AND** SHALL have `spec.versions[].name: v1alpha1`\n167: \n168: ### AR-001-017: CRD YAML generation for CodeInterpreter\n169: \n170: - **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreter` type with kubebuilder markers\n171: - **WHEN** running `make gen-crd`\n172: - **THEN** CRD YAML SHALL be generated in `manifests/charts/base/crds/`\n173: - **AND** SHALL have `name: codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n174: - **AND** SHALL have `spec.scope: Namespaced`\n175: - **AND** SHALL have `spec.versions[].name: v1alpha1`\n176: \n177: ### AR-001-018: CRD validation schema\n178: \n179: - **GIVEN** kubebuilder markers on type fields\n180: - **WHEN** generating CRD YAML\n181: - **THEN** validation rules SHALL be generated in OpenAPI v3 schema\n182: - **AND** `AgentRuntime.spec.maxSessionDuration` SHALL have validation (required, default \"8h\")\n183: - **AND** `CodeInterpreter.spec.authMode` SHALL have enum validation (picod, none)\n184: \n185: ---\n186: \n187: ## Scenario: Client-go Compatibility\n188: \n189: ### AR-001-019: Type name compatibility with client-go\n190: \n191: - **GIVEN** Go types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n192: - **WHEN** running `make gen-client`\n193: - **THEN** client-go SHALL be generated without type name conflicts\n194: - **AND** generated client SHALL expect `AgentRuntime` type (not `AgentRuntimeSpec` or other)\n195: - **AND** generated client SHALL expect `CodeInterpreter` type\n196: \n197: ### AR-001-020: List type compatibility\n198: \n199: - **GIVEN** Go types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n200: - **WHEN** running `make gen-client`\n201: - **THEN** `AgentRuntimeList` SHALL have `Items` field of type `[]AgentRuntime`\n202: - **AND** `CodeInterpreterList` SHALL have `Items` field of type `[]CodeInterpreter`\n203: \n204: ---\n205: \n206: ## Scenario: Build Verification\n207: \n208: ### AR-001-021: Go build succeeds\n209: \n210: - **GIVEN** complete type definitions in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n211: - **WHEN** running `go build ./pkg/apis/...`\n212: - **THEN** compilation SHALL succeed without errors\n213: - **AND** all types SHALL be properly importable\n214: \n215: ### AR-001-022: kubectl CRD apply\n216: \n217: - **GIVEN** generated CRD YAML files\n218: - **WHEN** applying to Kubernetes cluster with `kubectl apply -f`\n219: - **THEN** AgentRuntime CRD SHALL be created successfully\n220: - **AND** CodeInterpreter CRD SHALL be created successfully\n221: \n222: ---\n223: \n224: ## References\n225: \n226: - Base spec: `deployment/client-go.md`\n227: - Design: `proposal.md`\n228: - API Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n229: - Version: `v1alpha1`\n\n(End of file - total 229 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-001 ŌĆö CRD AgentRuntime ń▒╗Õ×ŗÕ«Üõ╣ē\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRD type definitions in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-001\n- **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n- **Base Spec**: `deployment/client-go.md` (client-go library types)\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: AgentRuntime Type Definition\n\n### AR-001-001: AgentRuntime type with required spec fields\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-001/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775852604419,"end":1775852604431}}}}
